  • Email mailboxes and folders appearing empty

    Some customers are reporting that their mailbox and folders are appearing empty. We are aware of this issue and are working to resolve it as soon as possible.

  • Problems accessing Tiscali email account

    Some customers may have issues accessing their Tiscali email accounts. Our engineers have identified that some email accounts may have been used to send large amounts of spam from our network.

  • Phishing email requesting you to update Email Account details

    Please be aware that a number of customers have reported that they have received an email pretending to be from TalkTalk. Please delete this email and do not follow any of the links.

  • Phishing email requesting to make payment.

    Please be aware that a number of customers have reported that they have received an email pretending to be from TalkTalk. Please delete this email and do not follow any of the links.

  • Being aware of phone scams

    Every year countless people are targeted by phone scammers and criminal organisations. Sadly this is a growing problem across all sectors. Here's some advice on how to stay safe.
